Class ButtonFreeCalendar

java.lang.Object
Vue.Calendar.ButtonFreeCalendar
Direct Known Subclasses:
ButtonImpossibleDay, ButtonOnDay, ButtonPromotionDay
public class ButtonFreeCalendar extends Object
ButtonFreeCalendar is a custom button class that provides a visual effect when the mouse hovers over it. It uses JavaFX's Timeline for animations.
